  Kernel::LessRotateCCW_2  


A model for this must provide:
 

    
         
    bool  

         
          
             
    fo.operator() (     
      Kernel::Point_2  p,  Kernel::Point_2  q,  Kernel::Point_2  r)     
                
    returns true iff the three points  p ,  q  
and  r  form a left turn or if they are  collinear  and
the distance of  q  to  p  is
larger than the distance of  r  to  p , where  p  is the point
passed to the object at construction.  Precondition:   p  does not lie in the interior of the segment  rq ,
i.e.Â  p  is an extreme point with respect to  {p,q,r} .
            

  Refines  AdaptableFunctor  (with three arguments)
 

